<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="content-h1"><h1>《咸池》</h1></div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="place">
<p id="openCatp" style="display:none">开放分类：<a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%90%E6%9B%B2/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="中国乐曲">中国乐曲</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E5%8F%A4%E5%85%B8%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="古典音乐">古典音乐</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="文化">文化</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="艺术">艺术</a><a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="音乐">音乐</a></p>
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="information" id="unifyprompt"><div class="summary" id="anchor" name="anchor"><p>《咸池》是一种古乐曲，相传为尧乐，也说为黄帝之乐，尧增修<a href="http://www.baike.com/wiki/%E6%B2%BF%E7%94%A8" target="_blank">沿用</a>。是一种表现宗教天神，歌颂的祭祀音乐。现已失传。</p><span><a action="editsummaryhref" href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="editSummary();return false;">编辑摘要</a></span>
</div></div>
